txt.en: 'Beyond the spiders, it seems that various gredbyg have also responded to the call of Shelob and taken up residence in Torech Ungol. Do not let your guard down; they are also dangerous in great numbers.'
The other children of Shelob, the Gredbyg, have also taken up residence in Torech Ungol.

'Did you defeat the gredbyg? Excellent work, [placeholder]. I know not how many more there are, or how deep they live inside. They may be Ungwet√°ri's children, but they are unlike the spiders in many ways, and pose different threats.'
Legolas is standing by outside Torech Ungol.\n\nYou should talk to Legolas.
Many gredbyg have responded to the call of Shelob and taken up residence in her lair.\n\nYou should defeat gredbyg inside Torech Ungol.
